00:32:14.215 --> 00:32:18.620 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‎living 
‎in these last days.

00:32:18.620 --> 00:32:21.956 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‎Jehovah knows 
‎that we need friends

00:32:21.956 --> 00:32:26.394 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‎to help us 
‎along the way.

00:32:26.394 --> 00:32:28.997 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‎But where do we go?

00:32:28.997 --> 00:32:35.103 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‎Where do we turn 
‎to find those true companions?

00:32:35.103 --> 00:32:43.544 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‎Well, remember what
‎we learn in his Word.

00:32:43.544 --> 00:32:47.248 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‎True friends
‎Love you when you’re down,

00:32:47.248 --> 00:32:53.287 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‎Happy when you’re up,
‎Right by your side when trials come,

00:32:53.287 --> 00:32:57.692 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‎Speak up if you’re wrong,
‎Commend you when you’re right,

00:32:57.692 --> 00:33:01.963 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‎Keep you on track 
‎in the race for life,

00:33:01.963 --> 00:33:07.735 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‎Help you keep 
‎Jehovah first right to the end.

00:33:07.735 --> 00:33:12.040 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‎Yeah, 
‎that’s a true friend.

00:33:17.145 --> 00:33:21.282 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‎A true friend 
‎shows love at all times.

00:33:21.282 --> 00:33:25.253 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‎That’s in His Word,
‎we know.

00:33:25.253 --> 00:33:29.891 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
‎So if troubles appear,
‎don’t give in or fight. 

00:33:29.891 --> 00:33:33.895 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
